# Client quotation sites

Skill: [`.cursor/skills/client-site-netlify/SKILL.md`](../skills/client-site-netlify/SKILL.md)  
**Catalog:** [`client-sites/README.md`](../../client-sites/README.md) — all deployed clients, preview links, contact, packages, outreach paths

## Preview showcase

- URL: `https://carlmanuel.com/?preview={slug}` (short id from `PREVIEW_SITES` / `client.json` → `slug`, e.g. `jk-construction`)
- Helper: `buildPreviewPortfolioUrl(slug)` in [`previewWhitelist.js`](../../src/v3/config/previewWhitelist.js)
- Tests: [`previewWhitelist.test.js`](../../src/v3/config/previewWhitelist.js), [`PreviewShowcase.test.js`](../../src/v3/containers/PreviewShowcase/PreviewShowcase.test.js), [`Index.test.js`](../../src/pages/Index.test.js)
- Whitelist: `*.netlify.app` OR explicit `PREVIEW_SITES` in [`previewWhitelist.js`](../../src/v3/config/previewWhitelist.js)
- Component: [`PreviewShowcase.js`](../../src/v3/containers/PreviewShowcase/PreviewShowcase.js)
- UI: desktop monitor + mobile phone mockups; iframes render at **1280×800** (desktop) and **390×844** (mobile), scaled to fit frames; **Back to portfolio** only (no live-site link)

## New client folder

1. Copy `client-sites/_template/` → `client-sites/{slug}/`
2. **Gather brief** from client Facebook via Chrome DevTools MCP (About + Photos); **inspect** images (dimensions, alt), **download** via `get_network_request` → `assets/` (not screenshots)
3. Customize `index.html` (Tailwind utilities), `styles.css` (hero/reveal only), `client.json`
3. Keep `site.js`, `embed-guard.js`, `netlify/edge-functions/embed-only.js`, and `netlify.toml` security headers
4. Deploy to Netlify; set `previewHost`, `deployedAt`, and `quotation.previewUrl` in `client.json`
5. Write outreach drafts: `quotation-email.md`, `quotation-sms.txt`, `quotation-messenger.txt`
6. Register in `PREVIEW_SITES`
7. **Update [`client-sites/README.md`](../../client-sites/README.md)** — add catalog table row + per-client detail section

## Outreach drafts (required per client)

| File | Use |
|------|-----|
| `quotation-email.md` | Formal email with subject, package table, preview link |
| `quotation-sms.txt` | Short SMS (~300 chars) |
| `quotation-messenger.txt` | FB Messenger, Viber, Telegram |

Pull package/price/contact from `client.json`. Present drafts to user for review — never auto-send.

## Post-deploy browser QA

After deploy, open `https://carlmanuel.com/?preview={slug}` and verify desktop + mobile mockups (scroll iframes, check header/hero at narrow width). Fix client `styles.css` and redeploy if layout breaks. See skill Step 7.

## Content guidelines

- Mobile-first, fast load (sales demo on phone matters).
- **Tailwind CDN + `site.js`** for interactive demos (mobile nav, accordions, tabs/filters, scroll reveal).
- Philippine/local business context OK (₱, Metro Manila, etc.).
- Fictitious demo businesses: label clearly (see `quotation/` sample).
- Outreach drafts: warm professional tone; ₱ pricing; Carl Louis Manuel sign-off.
- Match V3 greens for template consistency unless client has brand colors.

## Security

- Never iframe non-whitelisted domains on the portfolio.
- No API keys in `client-sites/` commits.
- **Embed-only client demos** — required on every site:
  - `embed-guard.js` (loaded in `<head>`)
  - `netlify/edge-functions/embed-only.js` + `[[edge_functions]]` in `netlify.toml`
  - CSP `frame-ancestors` for portfolio domains (+ `localhost:3000` for dev)
- Direct URL visits to client Netlify sites return **403**; content only loads in portfolio preview iframes.
- Do not add “open live site” links in `PreviewShowcase` or client HTML.

## Do not

- Commit Netlify auth tokens or `.netlify/` link state (gitignored)
- Remove or bypass embed-only guards without user approval
- Add real client PII without user approval (use placeholders in demos)
- Auto-send quotation email/SMS/messenger — drafts only until user approves
- Auto-add every client to public portfolio projects without user sign-off
